g-wolens-on-the-singularity-its-ultimately-up-to-you</link><description>&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/doug-wolens-on-the-singularity-its-ultimately-up-to-you2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jun 2026 16:08:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/doug-wolens-on-the-singularity-its-ultimately-up-to-you</guid></item><item><title>AI 重新利用常规胸部 X 光检查来发现骨折前无声的骨质流失</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/ai-repurposes-routine-chest-x-rays-to-catch-silent-bone-loss-before-fracture</link><description>骨质疏松症是一种无声的疾病，骨质流失在骨折发生之前逐渐发生。目前的临床筛查建议主要针对老年女性和选定的高危人群，而一些男性、年轻人和体重正常的人完全不在常规筛查途径之外。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/ai-repurposes-routine-chest-x-rays-to-catch-silent-bone-loss-before-fracture2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jun 2026 15:53:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/ai-repurposes-routine-chest-x-rays-to-catch-silent-bone-loss-before-fracture</guid></item><item><title>人工智能网络威胁推动零信任安全转变</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/ai-cyber-threats-drive-zero-trust-security-shift</link><description>经过&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/ai-cyber-threats-drive-zero-trust-security-shift.jpg" /&gt; 由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jun 2026 15:38:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/ai-cyber-threats-drive-zero-trust-security-shift</guid></item><item><title>量子前沿：量子计算如何重塑我们的未来</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/the-quantum-frontier-how-quantum-computing-is-reshaping-our-future</link><description>量子计算曾经被认为是一个遥远的科学项目，可以彻底改变计算。今天，这种讨论发生了巨大变化。量子技术的进步已经超越了实验室试验和理论。新兴的量子能力包括商业量子平台、量子网络项目、量子传感器的进步和强大的量子处理器。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/the-quantum-frontier-how-quantum-computing-is-reshaping-our-future.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jun 2026 15:23:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/the-quantum-frontier-how-quantum-computing-is-reshaping-our-future</guid></item><item><title>重塑药物发现的未来</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/reshaping-the-future-of-drug-discovery</link><description>韩国的一项创新资助计划的雄心勃勃的目标是通过追求前所未有的治疗方法来扩大潜在“可成药”蛋白质靶标的范围。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/reshaping-the-future-of-drug-discovery.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jun 2026 15:08:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/reshaping-the-future-of-drug-discovery</guid></item><item><title>流行的关节补充剂葡萄糖胺与阿尔茨海默病的加速进展有关</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/popular-joint-supplement-glucosamine-linked-to-faster-alzheimers-progression</link><description>由于葡萄糖胺广泛存在，并且经常被老年人用来支持关节健康，因此研究人员希望确定它是否会影响阿尔茨海默病和相关痴呆症 (ADRD)。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/popular-joint-supplement-glucosamine-linked-to-faster-alzheimers-progression.webp" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jun 2026 14:53:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/popular-joint-supplement-glucosamine-linked-to-faster-alzheimers-progression</guid></item><item><title>养殖池爆发肉毒杆菌病导致虹鳟鱼大量损失</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/botulism-outbreak-at-rearing-pond-leads-to-large-loss-of-rainbow-trout</link><description>本周早些时候，由于梅森县 WDFW 孵化场的养殖池爆发肉毒杆菌中毒，近 167,000 条虹鳟鱼不得不被送往私人垃圾填埋场，而不是当地湖泊。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/botulism-outbreak-at-rearing-pond-leads-to-large-loss-of-rainbow-trout.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jun 2026 14:38:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/botulism-outbreak-at-rearing-pond-leads-to-large-loss-of-rainbow-trout</guid></item></channel></rss>